metadata.name: XPHY55.01 Jack of Hearts
metadata.description:
Piece 01 of 55 of the XPHYEE 55 collection, the Jack of Hearts.

Trailer for the 55 collection: 
https://youtu.be/ScpG3YOvwXg

Originally minted as XPHY pre XPHYEE name change.

This is the first ever XPHYEE NFT, originally minted on 14 March 2021, re-minted here off the OS storefront contract.
